name: save_contact
description: Save the contact being created or edited.

name: cancel_editing
description: Cancel the current contact editing process and discard changes.

name: add_contact_photo
description: Add a photo to the contact.

name: fill_in_name
description: Enter the first and last name of the contact.
parameters: {'first_name': "What is the contact's first name?", 'last_name': "What is the contact's last name?"}

name: show_more_name_fields
description: Expand to show additional name-related fields.

name: fill_in_company
description: Enter the company name associated with the contact.

name: fill_in_phone
description: Enter the phone number of the contact.

name: select_phone_type
description: Select the type of the phone number (e.g., Mobile).
parameters: {'phone_type': 'What is the type of the phone number? [Mobile]'}

name: fill_in_email
description: Enter the email address of the contact.

name: select_email_type
description: Select the type of the email address (e.g., Home).
parameters: {'email_type': 'What is the type of the email address? [Home]'}

name: show_date_picker
description: Open the date picker to select a significant date for the contact.

name: show_dropdown_menu
description: Show a dropdown menu for additional options.
